title: DC Historic District Polygons
name: DC Historic District Polygons
description: This dataset contains Historic Districts officially designated by the District of Columbia and National Historical Sites & National Historical Parks within the District of Columbia. Additional data sets are also available providing information on (1) other areas of historic significance in the District of Columbia and (2) historic structures in the District of Columbia. The same records in this polygon-format dataset are also available in a point-format dataset.
